{{Flavour|Translocates the caster to a location further away from a targeted enemy, but still within sight of the target.}}

'''Blink Range''' is a monster-only spell which causes the caster [[blink]], always leaving the caster a moderate distance from you, perfect for pelting you with their ranged attacks.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.26]], [[pandemonium lord]]s couldn't cast this spell.

